(:name evil-numbers
       :website "http://github.com/cofi/evil-numbers"
       :description "Increment/decrement numbers in Evil, the extensible vim
       emulation layer. Like C-a/C-x in vim.

       After installation, you will need to add a key-binding for evil-numbers.
       For example:

       (define-key evil-normal-state-map (kbd \"C-c +\") 'evil-numbers/inc-at-pt)
       (define-key evil-normal-state-map (kbd \"C-c -\") 'evil-numbers/dec-at-pt)"

       :type git
       :url "http://github.com/cofi/evil-numbers.git"
       :features evil-numbers
       :depends evil)
